00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:41,840
You're looking at this too naively.
你把问题想得太简单了。

182
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:45,840
The Chinese market has exhibited a great deal of instability, and their currency has been
中国市场表现出很大的不稳定性，而且他们的货币已经

